# Quote style: straight quotes only

Use **straight (ASCII) quotes** only in this repo. Do not introduce or leave **smart/curly typographic quotes**.

## Allowed

- Single quote: `'` (U+0027)
- Double quote: `"` (U+0022)

## Avoid

- Left/right single quotation marks: `‘` `’` (U+2018, U+2019)
- Left/right double quotation marks: `“` `”` (U+201C, U+201D)

## Why

Straight quotes ensure consistent string matching in search-and-replace, configs, and scripts across editors and tools.

## When editing

- Type or paste using straight `'` and `"`.
- If you normalize existing content, replace any curly/smart quotes with the corresponding straight character.
